Basic description: Improves your resistance to fire and cold.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=3582&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Whizbang's notes: Our next to last upgrade in this line, and a not insignifcant amount of protection. Its extremely long duration is a nice bonus. This also stacks with the druidic Circle of Seasons, which our upgrade does not, which affords an even higher level of protection, assuming you can afford the multiple buff slots.<br>
Spell era: Planes of Power<br>
Vendor information: The Plane of Knowledge, Myrist, Channeler Keatrem<br>
Research information: This spell cannot be researched.<br>
Quest information: This spell is not a quest reward in any known quests.<br>
Drop information: This spell is not dropped by any known NPC.<br>
<br>
Familiar<br>
Basic description: Conjures forth a familiar that adds to a wizard's abilities.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2557&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Whizbang's notes: Our first familiar spell to summon a black drake instead of a red imp, and our first familiar spell to add mana regeneration to an already nice package of effects. Note that typing &quot;/pet get lost&quot; gets rid of the familiar while retaining all the benefits of the spell. For more information on familiars, see <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.arcanist.com/modules.php?name=Reviews&rop=showcontent&id=18">www.arcanist.com/modules....tent&id=18</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Spell era: Shadows of Luclin<br>
Vendor information: This spell is not sold by any known NPC.<br>
Research information: This spell cannot be researched.<br>
Quest information: This spell is not a quest reward in any known quests.<br>
Drop information: Various Luclin NPCs.<br>
<br>
Pillar of Lightning<br>
Basic description: A targeted area of effect spell, lightning based, that hits up to four targets.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1645&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Whizbang's notes: The next to last quadding upgrade.<br>
Spell era: Ruins of Kunark<br>
Vendor information: This spell is not sold by any known NPC.<br>
Research information: Sorcerer's Lexicon, Parchment, Quill, Rune of Alteration, Rune of Gale<br>
Quest information: This spell is not a quest reward in any known quests.<br>
Drop information: Various Kunark NPCs.<br>
<br>
Shield of the Magi<br>
Basic description: This spell creates an invisible field of energy around you, raising hit points, armor class and magic resistance.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1610&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Whizbang's notes: The last of the pre-planar shielding upgrades, this is another solid spell in the line.<br>
Spell era: Ruins of Kunark<br>
Vendor information: <br>
Firiona Vie, Selien Nartoise<br>
The Overthere, Tyrin F'Linz<br>
The Plane of Knowledge, Myrist, Channeler Olaemos<br>
Research information: This spell cannot be researched.<br>
Quest information: This spell is not a quest reward in any known quests.<br>
Drop information: This spell is not dropped by any known NPC.<br>
<br>
Thunderbold<br>
Basic description: This spell radiates a stunning blast of lightning out of you, striking every NPC nearby.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1656&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Whizbang's notes: An upgrade to Thunderclap. Note that it has a knockback effect.<br>
Spell era: Ruins of Kunark<br>
Vendor information: This spell is not sold by any known NPC.<br>
Research information: This spell cannot be researched.<br>
Quest information: <br>
Fironia Vie, Barnal Flamehand<br>
The Overthere, Utandar Rizndown<br>
Drop information: This spell is not dropped by any known NPC.<br>
<br>
Voltaic Draught<br>
Basic description: This spell releases a rapid burst of lightning, striking a single target.<br>
Raw data: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1639&source=Live">lucy.fnord.net/spell.html...ource=Live</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Whizbang's notes: Our second draught does the same damage as the workhorse Draught of Fire, but can hit things immune to fire. Useful in the Skyfire Mountains, for instance.<br>
Spell era: Ruins of Kunark<br>
Vendor information: <br>
Firiona Vie, Selien Nartoise<br>
The Overthere, Tyrin F'Linz<br>
The Plane of Knowledge, Myrist, Channeler Olaemos<br>
Research information: This spell cannot be researched.<br>
